        <b>How do I change my password?</b>
        <p>The "Account" tab on the navigation bar is where you'll find information about your TaskCenter profile. There,
             you can also update pieces of information such as email, username, and password.</p><br>
        
        <b>How do I delete a calendar?</b>
        <p>At the lower lefthand corner of each calendar besides the default calendar, there's a red button that 
            enables deletion of a calendar. The default calendar cannot be deleted.</p><br>

        <b>How do I share a calendar with another user?</b>
        <p>At the upper righthand corner of each calendar, there's a blue button labeled "Share" which
            gives the user options to grant another user access to the calendar. It's necessary to know the username of the 
            user who you want to share a calendar with.</p><br>

